snippet.title: Terror of the Catacombs gameplay (PC Game, 1993)
snippet.description:
Introduction and gameplay for Terror of the Catacombs, Dos PC game produced by Froggman in 1993 - http://www.squakenet.com/download/terror-of-the-catacombs/14413/
Terror of the Catacombs is a pretty nice game. You're a mag whose quest is to destroy the evil Nemesis, you can throw fireballs at your foes or use them to destroy certain walls.
Played through Dosbox emulation platform.
Recorded with original sound.

Similar videos you may like:
Curse of the Catacombs - https://youtu.be/srmSeSJ7EKw
The Fortress of Dr. Radiaki - https://youtu.be/_4WhSh7Xsyo
Catacomb 3D - https://youtu.be/_hynUBhvXhY
